lass=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T08:01:19.000Z","msg":"次次冬季講響公司講呀爸呀媽打流感針，我同事都講佢樓下既看更打完幾日後發燒走左，仲兩個，50幾歲又唔係好老呀。<br />\n東張西望果個你可以睇番東張西望。"},{"pid":"963d4b62670e87f709ba36a58b5da1282f44467b","tid":2255164,"uid":115579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T08:45:35.000Z","msg":"本身死嘅多數都係老野"},{"pid":"bcf5495befc4298f0a8193eea8966b0e979638c5","tid":2255164,"uid":110562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T11:38:06.000Z","msg":"打疫苗不嬲有風險 特別老人"},{"pid":"dff4fc8734d3b0706c17bd1c5a323a3ce620f126","tid":2255164,"uid":76804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T08:49:08.000Z","msg":"59個<br />\n又黎廢老清洗<br />\n<br />\n據韓媒報導，韓國疾病管理廳26日表示，截至當地時間當日0時，累計已有59人接種流感疫苗後死亡。在此情況下，韓國疾病管理廳仍表示，死亡與接種疫苗間的關聯性很低，決定繼續按計畫進行接種。<br />\n<br />\n從年齡段來看，韓國接受相關疫苗接種後的死者中，70多歲和80多歲的各26人，人數最多；60多歲的2人，不到60歲的5人。"},{"pid":"4168ec3675c283daa54517d34422365cda9976c1","tid":2255164,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T09:00:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20140117/large/1389946314_4a6b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20140117%2Flarge%2F1389946314_4a6b.jpg&h=e0a5a0fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/oSX_TPWZ4IA/hqdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FoSX_TPWZ4IA%2Fhqdefault.jpg&h=84da01a5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f36106c5494336830de1e9414b4374b11f8823d1","tid":2255164,"uid":126947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T09:01:16.000Z","msg":"上年識6x幾歲長輩打完入咗廠<br />\n好彩無事出番嚟<br />\n之後都唔敢再打"},{"pid":"4e283fa5cb2bf3b195c64c9a02e8e6ffefaaf041","tid":2255164,"uid":159448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T10:18:42.000Z","msg":"新加坡即刻停左韓國疫苗"}]}